Content: Arkivar Team
Explore Settings with Web Browser iPhone and Android Phone to discover persistency or concurrency errors
Download and extract https://github.com/IMSmobile/app/archive/0.12.1.zip
Change into directory and run ''npm install''
Run command ''ionic cordova run browser'' / start app
Open browser to http://localhost:8000/
Browser: Splash screen is missing logo
Login with account ''mia''
Select archive
Navigate to settings page
Check search in ''Bildupload Felder''
Enter ''k''
Three fields displayed on all devices
Enter ''*'' as search text as wildcard
No results
Enter ''test'' and press ''x'' (clear) button
All fields reappeard
iPhone only: Keyboard dissapears and reappears when clicking ''x''
Quickly click toggle button multiple times
Verify correct fields are active on upload page
Fields successfully shown on all devices
Disable URL field
Server Field is not displayed on all devices
Disable URL Field and immediately logout
Server Field is not displayed on all devices
Select all fields in ''Einträge Felder''
Compare entries list on all devices
Android Phone: scrolling in entries becomes very slow
iPhone: scrolling in entries results in app crash
Arkivar Team
Explore Upload with Web Browser iPhone and Android Phone to discover field validation
Same as in charter before
Start fresh browser in private mode
Login with account ''mia''
configure ''Bidlupload Felder'' of each type: DATETIMEFELD; BOOLEANYES; FLOATFELD; DATEFELD; INTEGERFELD; KEYWORDDUAL; KEYWORDSINGLE; TIMEFELD; TEXTFELD
Verify fields appear on upload page of a entry
DATETIMEFELD select and press cancel
Field stays empty on all devices
iPhone and Android Phone: year in DATETIME selection is not fully visible in portrait mode
DATETIMEFELD: Select 01.02.2003 04:06:06
Enter something into the mandatory field and press upload
Upload was successful on all devices
Date has arrived at IMS server
Time is in UTC; not local time
Select BOOLEANYES field to enable it
upload was successfull on all devices; BOOLEANYES field data was received by IMS server
FLOADFELD: enter ''abc'' as value and try to upload
All devices show warning about invalid fields
FLOATFELD: enter ''12.a'' as value and try to upload
All devices show warning about invalid fields
FLOATFELD: enter '' '' (space) as value and try to upload
FLOATFELD: Validation accepts '' '' (space) as a valid value
FLOATFELD: Error appears on all devices
Upload was successful on all devices
Value is truncated the same from all devices on IMS server
DATEFIELD: enter ''31.12.1917'' as value and try to upload
Upload was successful on all devices; DATEFIELD field data was received by IMS server
INTEGERFELD: enter ''0'' (zero) as value
INTEGERFELD: upload was successful on all devices and value is the same on IMS server
INTEGERFELD: enter ''-9999999999999'' as value
Upload fails on all devices with error
INTEGERFELD: enter ''ninethousand'' as value
validation check appears on all devices
KEYWORDDUAL: double tap/click on field
iPhone and Android Phone: keywordselection page is loaded twice
May be fixed by #592
KEYWORDDUAL: select ''99.'' as value
Upload was successful on all devices; KEYWORDDUAL field data has arrived on IMS server
Arkivar does not upload keyword fields the same as the full IMS client (only the last value; not with the full path)
KEYWORDSINGLE: select ''Radhaus hinten rechts'' as value
upload from all devices sucessful; KEYWORDSINGLE field data has arrived on IMS server
TIMEFELD: use ''23:59:59'' as value
all devices uploaded successfully; value arrived correctly at IMS server
TEXTFELD: enter very long string
Android Phone: field is not visible at all
iPhone: field only visible when starting to type
Browser: error appears when copying 100000 words into field
iPhone: text is hidden by big green upload button
Time is up; good work everyone!
